    <div class="container">
        <h1>Returns & Replacements</h1>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Return Policy</h2>
            <p>Most items can be returned within 30 days of receipt for a full refund. Items must be in original condition with packaging intact.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>Replacement Process</h2>
            <p>If you receive a defective or damaged product, you can request a replacement within 10 days of delivery.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq">
            <h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
            <p><strong>Q: How do I return a product?</strong></p>
            <p>A: Go to your orders, select the item, and choose the return option.</p>
            <p><strong>Q: When will I get my refund?</strong></p>
            <p>A: Refunds are processed within 5-7 business days after we receive your return.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact">
            <a href="/customer-service">Contact Customer Support</a>
        </div>
    </div>
